Hey, wanderer. Careful.

48:34.640 --> 48:38.952
Watch may, but not touch.

48:40.120 --> 48:42.543
What did I say?
- It's beautiful.

48:42.720 --> 48:45.860
Of course, everything I have is beautiful.

48:46.560 --> 48:48.983
A masterpiece.
- Masterpiece?

48:49.160 --> 48:54.268
Yes, made in the Netherlands.
The land of the tulips.

48:54.440 --> 48:56.226
Costs only 5000.

48:56.400 --> 48:59.790
