53:09.440 --> 53:11.499
Money, money.

53:48.600 --> 53:50.033
Waiter...

53:52.520 --> 53:55.148
A bottle of Prosecco, please.

53:55.320 --> 53:58.346
Thank you.
And a room with a bath.

54:09.760 --> 54:11.034
Please.

54:13.000 --> 54:14.103
Thank you.

56:24.880 --> 56:26.393
Thank you.
- Please.

59:54.400 --> 59:56.948
Hello, welcome back.

59:57.120 --> 01:00:00.078
How are you?
- Great, now that I see you.

01:00:00.240 --> 01:00:01.946
Very well.

01:00:02.440 --> 01:00:04.988
The painting, 3500.

01:00:05.160 --> 01:00:08.186
3500? That's what I do it for.

01:00:08.840 --> 01:00:12.037
Please.
- Thank you, friend.

01:00:12.520 --> 01:00:14.875
And greetings to your wife.

01:01:40.840 --> 01:01:43.138
